lpf (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Split policy into types, formatter, and parser modules.
  * New lpf sysctl check|diff subcommand with generated man page.
  * Expanded sysctl coverage to include rp_filter and bridge-nf parameters.
  * Pipeline.preimage_info delegates TC/routing extraction from apply_guard.
  * Bash completion for all 18 subcommands and options.
  * Docker dev environment with OCaml 5.1, iproute2, nftables, conntrack.
  * 30 policy round-trip tests and JSON fuzz tests.
  * OCamlformat normalization for dune files.

 -- lpf maintainers <lpf@example.com>  Thu, 18 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000

lpf (0.1.3-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Multi-backend rollback with nftables, TC, routing, and sysctl restore.
  * New sysctl module with snapshot, restore, and diff support.
  * Robust conntrack delete now accepts optional sport/dport filters.
  * Integration test suite with 34 new tests for ip, sysctl, and conntrack.
  * CI man page freshness check and OCamlformat integration.

